title: NFL Week 6 Picks Against the Spread, Best Bets, Predictions and Previews (Football 10/14)
description:
Will Brinson, Pete Prisco, and R.J. White give their expert takes and best bets for every week 6 NFL matchup. 

Intro (0:00)
Ravens at Giants  (5:30)
Bengals at Saints (7:30)
Jaguars at Colts (10:30)
Vikings at Dolphins (17:30)
Bills at Chiefs (20:10)
Cowboys at Eagles  (25:15)
Broncos at Chargers  (28:50)
Panthers at Rams  (32:14)
Cardinals at Seahawks  (38:00)
49ers at Falcons  (45:16)
Jets at Packers  (46:50)
Bucs at Steelers  (50:22)
Patriots at Browns  (51:26)
